            <p class="subtitle">Rapid bedside tool to systematically assess delirium using validated instruments (CAM-ICU, 4AT), guide evidence-based workup for reversible causes, and document safe management decisions including non-pharmacologic interventions and escalation triggers.</p>
        </header>

