                    If severe agitation threatens safety: haloperidol 0.5‚Äì1 mg IV/PO or quetiapine 12.5‚Äì25 mg PO (see local protocol; avoid in QTc >500 ms, Parkinson's). Avoid benzodiazepines except alcohol/sedative withdrawal (NICE CG103, SCCM Guidelines).
                </div>
