                    <h2>‚ö†Ô∏è Escalation Criteria</h2>
                    <button class="help-btn" onclick="toggleHelp('escalation-help')">‚ÑπÔ∏è Info</button>
                </div>
                <div id="escalation-help" class="help-text">
                    Check any criteria that apply. Any checked item should prompt urgent escalation to senior clinician, rapid response, or ICU consultation.
